Description : Style for books

Doc Class   : book
Package*    : fancyhdr
Tex Header* :
  \fancyhead[LE,RO]{\thepage}
  \fancyhead[LO]{\nouppercase\rightmark}
  \fancyhead[RE]{\nouppercase\leftmark}
  \fancyfoot{}
  \fancypagestyle{plain}{%
     \fancyhf{}%
     \renewcommand\headrulewidth{0pt}%
  }
  \pagestyle{fancy}

@if tex {
  Heading Base: 1
  h1 { before: clear }
}